                     <note type="paleography">The text is is written along the fibers in relatively large-sized cursive letters with ligatures; the hand is elegant and adorned. The omicron at the beginning is semi-complete circle; the epsilon is 2 halves circles attached together; even interlinear spaces. No abbreviations are attested. The verso has some unclear writings with different hand.</note>
