                  <objectDesc>
                     <p>
                        <note type="conservation">This papyrus has the left and op margins; regularly cut at the left side; broken off at the right and bottom. There are some lacunae, especially at the right side; there are also some blots of dirt on several parts of recto and verso. Some fibers are removed from the verso. There is 1Kollesis at the right side of recto.</note>
